messages.msgSnippet: THanks, she s enjoying it.  THe funniest is when we go somewhere. I forget there is something different about her and we re walking  along and all these people
messages.messageBody:
THanks, she's enjoying it. THe funniest is when we go somewhere. I
forget there is something different about her and we're walking along
and all these people are looking and I'm thinking, are my clothes on, is
my zipper unzipped, why are they staring, and then I remember, oh yeah,
Lexie's hair is a brilliant blue!

Joylyn
